Paper: hep-th/9703081

Date: 1997-03-11

Title: Quantization of the complex linear superfield

Authors: M. Grisaru, A. Van Proeyen and D. Zanon

Comments: 21 pages, latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B502 (1997) 345-362

The quantization of the complex linear superfield requires an infinite towerof ghosts. We use the Batalin-Vilkovisky method to obtain a gauge-fixed action.In superspace, the method brings in some novel features.